    <h1>Keyword Density</h1>
    <p class="description">The percentage of times a target keyword appears in content relative to total word count. Once central to SEO, now a guardrail metric — <strong>too low is a miss, too high is a penalty</strong>, and the sweet spot is natural language.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
